	<h1 id="firstHeading" class="firstHeading" lang="en">Games/MineClone 2/Differences from Minetest Game</h1>
	<div id="bodyContent" class="mw-body-content">
		<div id="siteSub" class="noprint">From Minetest Wiki</div>
