<p>For players familar with <a href="/Games/Minetest_Game" title="Games/Minetest Game">Minetest Game</a>, 
this is a list of differences when playing <a href="/Games/MineClone_2" title="Games/MineClone 2">MineClone 2</a>&#160;:
</p><p>(As observed on <a rel="nofollow" class="external text" href="https://forum.minetest.net/viewtopic.php?f=10&amp;t=19974">Mark Server - MC2-Survival</a>, 2019-12 .. 2020-04,
then reset+restarted with a new map)
</p>
<div id="toc" class="toc" role="navigation" aria-labelledby="mw-toc-heading"><input type="checkbox" role="button" id="toctogglecheckbox" class="toctogglecheckbox" style="display:none" /><div class="toctitle" lang="en" dir="ltr"><h2 id="mw-toc-heading">Contents</h2><span class="toctogglespan"><label class="toctogglelabel" for="toctogglecheckbox"></label></span></div>
